<li id="cite_note-29"><b><a href="#cite_ref-29" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://online.wsj.com/article/SB122516435782975265.html" class="external free" title="http://online.wsj.com/article/SB122516435782975265.html" rel="nofollow">http://online.wsj.com/article/SB122516435782975265.html</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-30"><b><a href="#cite_ref-30" title="">^</a></b> Massaldi, Julian, <a href="http://www.zmag.org/content/showarticle.cfm?ItemID=4536" class="external text" title="http://www.zmag.org/content/showarticle.cfm?ItemID=4536" rel="nofollow">"Buenos Aires Consensus: Lula and Kirchner's agreement 'Against Neoliberalism'"</a>, Znet, November 20, 2003</li>
<li id="cite_note-31"><b><a href="#cite_ref-31" title="">^</a></b> See, e.g., Financial Times at following link: <a href="http://www.ft.com/cms/s/d62ca1a2-c219-11db-ae23-000b5df10621.html" class="external free" title="http://www.ft.com/cms/s/d62ca1a2-c219-11db-ae23-000b5df10621.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.ft.com/cms/s/d62ca1a2-c219-11db-ae23-000b5df10621.html</a>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-32"><b><a href="#cite_ref-32" title="">^</a></b> New York Times, 2007 December 2, "Ending Famine, Simply by Ignoring the Experts," <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/02/world/africa/02malawi.html?em&amp;ex=1196744400&amp;en=8dc6209db5ec0efe&amp;ei=5087%0A" class="external free" title="http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/02/world/africa/02malawi.html?em&amp;ex=1196744400&amp;en=8dc6209db5ec0efe&amp;ei=5087%0A" rel="nofollow">http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/02/world/africa/02malawi.html?em&amp;ex=1196744400&amp;en=8dc6209db5ec0efe&amp;ei=5087%0A</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-33"><b><a href="#cite_ref-33" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://blogs.cgdev.org/globaldevelopment/2007/12/the_value_of_rejecting_expert_1.php" class="external text" title="http://blogs.cgdev.org/globaldevelopment/2007/12/the_value_of_rejecting_expert_1.php" rel="nofollow">Global Development: Views from the Center: The Value of Rejecting Expert Advice</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-34"><b><a href="#cite_ref-34" title="">^</a></b> New York Times, 2007 December 2, “Ending Famine, Simply by Ignoring the Experts,” <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/02/world/africa/02malawi.html?em&amp;ex=1196744400&amp;en=8dc6209db5ec0efe&amp;ei=5087%0A" class="external free" title="http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/02/world/africa/02malawi.html?em&amp;ex=1196744400&amp;en=8dc6209db5ec0efe&amp;ei=5087%0A" rel="nofollow">http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/02/world/africa/02malawi.html?em&amp;ex=1196744400&amp;en=8dc6209db5ec0efe&amp;ei=5087%0A</a></li>
