<li id="cite_note-36"><b><a href="#cite_ref-36" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://econ161.berkeley.edu/Politics/Fischer_Asia.html" class="external text" title="http://econ161.berkeley.edu/Politics/Fischer_Asia.html" rel="nofollow">Stanley Fischer on the IMF and East Asia</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-37"><b><a href="#cite_ref-37" title="">^</a></b> See, as examples representative of a much more extensive literature, e.g., Birdsall and de la Torre. "Washington Contentious" (2003); Kuczynski and Williamson (eds.), "After the Washington Consensus" (2003).</li>
